Variable Object Properties

Property Description
Class Identifier Returns a string that uniquely identifies the class to which the variable object belongs. Details
Engine Returns a reference to the variable engine to which the variable object belongs. Details
Name Returns the name of the variable object. Details
Parent Returns a reference to the variable container in which the variable object resides. Details
Readable Indicates whether the variable object includes a readable data value. Details
URL Returns the URL that identifies the variable object. Details
Writable Indicates whether the variable object includes a writable data value. Details
